            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">The Cultural Mosaic of East India</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-10">
                East India encompasses the states of West Bengal, Odisha, Bihar, Jharkhand, and the Seven Sisters of the Northeast.
                This region, cradled by the mighty rivers Ganges and Brahmaputra, is a melting pot of cultures,
                where ancient traditions blend with colonial influences, creating a unique cultural identity.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md text-center">
